 786:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** /**
 787:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @brief Configure the main regulator output voltage.
 788:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @param  VoltageScaling specifies the regulator output voltage to achieve
 789:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         a tradeoff between performance and power consumption.
 790:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         This parameter can be one of the following values:
 791:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *          @arg @ref PWR_REGULATOR_VOLTAGE_SCALE1 Regulator voltage output range 1 mode,
 792:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *                                                typical output voltage at 1.2 V,
 793:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *                                                system frequency up to 64 MHz.
 794:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *          @arg @ref PWR_REGULATOR_VOLTAGE_SCALE2 Regulator voltage output range 2 mode,
 795:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *                                                typical output voltage at 1.0 V,
 796:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *                                                system frequency up to 16 MHz.
 797:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note  When moving from Range 1 to Range 2, the system frequency must be decreased to
 798:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        a value below 16 MHz before calling HAL_PWREx_ControlVoltageScaling() API.
 799:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        When moving from Range 2 to Range 1, the system frequency can be increased to
 800:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        a value up to 64 MHz after calling HAL_PWREx_ControlVoltageScaling() API.
 801:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note  When moving from Range 2 to Range 1, the API waits for VOSF flag to be
 802:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        cleared before returning the status. If the flag is not cleared within
 803:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        6 microseconds, HAL_TIMEOUT status is reported.
 804:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @retval HAL Status
 805:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   */
